The paper deals with topics related to information theory (cs.IT) such as Kolmogorov complexity, as well as computational complexity (cs.CC) and data structures (cs.DS) in the context of prefix-free complexity. The paper also discusses results related to cryptography (cs.CR) and logic (cs.LO).
